  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AngleDegreesFromCamera
    Turns the robot until the angle is reached using the camera
    AutonomousCameraTargetingLeftCommandGroup
    Rotation for targeting with camera from left
    AutonomousCameraTargetingRightCommandGroup
    Rotation for targeting with camera from the right
    AutonomousDelayCommand
    Delays the robot for a set amount of time.
    AutonomousDriveBackwardCommand
    Drives the bot backwards until a new command is called
    AutonomousDriveForwardCommand
    Drives the bot forwards until a new command is called
    AutonomousRangedDriveForwardCommand
    Drives the bot forward until a specified range is met
    AutonomousRotateIntCommand
    Rotates the bot a set amount of degrees
    AutonomousTargetingLeftCommandGroup
    Autonomous from middle with switch on left using targeting
    AutonomousTargetingRightCommandGroup
    Autonomous from middle with switch on right using targeting
    AutonomousTimedDriveForward
    Drives the bot forwards for a set amount of time
    AutonomousTurnLeftCommand
    Turns the bot left until another command is called
    AutonomousTurnRightCommand
    Turns the bot right until another command is called
    ClawDownCommand
    Puts the claw down
    CloseGripperCommand
    Closes the gripper
    ControlManipulatorCommand
    Runs the method from the Manipulator Susbsystem that controls all aspects of the bot not related to the drivetrain and used during teleop mode
    LiftUpCommand
    Lifts up the left for a set amount of time
    LLAutonomousLeftCommandGroup
    Autonomous from left with near switch and scale on left
    OpenGripperCommand
    Opens the gripper
    RangeFinderFindDistanceInInchesCommand Deprecated.
    Puts the value of the rangefinder on the smartdashboard
    RRAutonomousRightCommandGroup
    Autonomous from right with switch on right
    StopMovingCommand
    Stops the drivetrain from moving
    TalonRampOffCommand Deprecated.
    Turns the ramp present on the talons off
    TalonRampOnCommand Deprecated.
    Turns ramp present on the Talon on
    TestCommandDontHateMeTaylor
    Exactly what it says.
    XboxDriveCommand
    Maps the values of the joysticks to the talons via the tankDrive method
